quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,Ha Mim
  43,2,Nditsuba khushitabu shinoosinjia
  43,3,Toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani mulwarabu kho munyoole okhumanya
  43,4,"Ne toto eyo ili nende amaandiko karula khwifwe, niyoluyali eyamachesi"
  43,5,"Koo khuleshe okhubetsulisia mana khwibilile, mbu shichila muli Abandu babura eshichelo"
  43,6,Ne ni Abarumwa benga bakhwaranjilila okhuruma khubandu bakhale
  43,7,Ne abulaho Omurumwa yesiyesi wabetselanga okhuula bamukholelanga omubayo
  43,8,Ne khwasishia balia abali nende amaani okhushila bo. Ne okhuchelaasia khwa Abandu ba khale khwamala okhubura
  43,9,"Ne nobareba mbu: “ niwina waloonga likulu nende eshialo?” Toto balaboola mbu: “wabiloonga Owamaani Omumanyi muno”"
  43,10,"Ulia wabakwalasilia liloba shinga obulili, nabarereramwo tsinjila khomunyoole okhulunjikha"
  43,11,"Niye wishinjia amaatsi okhurula mwikulu khushichelo, nikhulamusilia liloba liafwa, ne endio nilwa mulirusibwamwo"
  43,12,"Ne niye owaloonga buli eshindu eshisatsa nende eshikhasi, mana nabakasilia ebininwamwo biomumaatsi, nende tsisolo tsiamuninangakhwo"
  43,13,"Kho mwikhale obulayi khu mikongo chiatsio, mana mwitsulile tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wenyu, nimwakhamala okhwikhalakhwo\tobulayi,\tmana muboole mbu: “uluyaali nilwa ulia owakhukwalasilia bino mbu khwikhonyele, ne shikhwakhakholele abeene kano tawe .”"
  43,14,Ne toto khulikalukha ewa Nyasaye wefu Omulesi
  43,15,"Ne bamukholelenga mubasumba bebe omukabo, toto Omundu nomukhayi owahabulafu Owetsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye"
  43,16,"Nohomba yebukulila Abana abakhaana mubiloonje bibie biayaloonga, mana nabawulila enywe Abana abasiani"
  43,17,"Ne yesi yesi mubo naboolelwa khukabachelasinjiakhwo Nyasaye , obweni bubwe bumaliyanga ne yetsulamwo oburuma"
  43,18,"Koo ulia wakhusibwa muburone, ne shanyala okhuboola niyenoosia tawe"
  43,19,Ne bakhola Abamalaika abaali abasumba ba Nyasaye okhuba abakhasi! Koo balolakhwo okhulongwa khwabu? obuloli bwabu bulihandikwa ne balireebwa
  43,20,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “ Nyasaye yenyanga efwe shikhwakhabalaamile tawe.” Shibamanyile ako tawe. Babula liababoola halali obubeyi butswa"
  43,21,Khwabahelesiakhwo eshitabu imbeli wa shino? Mana batilananga ninashio bashiloondanga
  43,22,"Halali baboola mbu: “toto efwe khwanyoola bapapa befu nibaloondanga idini yabu yabalobola kho efwe khuloondanga mubilenje biabu.”"
  43,23,"Ne endio shikhwarumakhwo embeli wuwo omwikanyilisi mulukongo lwosi lwosi halali balia bali mubwokholo baboola mbu: “efwe khwanyoola bapapa befu nibaloondanga idini yabu yabalobola nafu khuloondanga mubilenje biabu”"
  43,24,"Naboola mbu: “kata nebarerera kobulunjifuobulayiokhushilabiamwanyoola basenywe Nibali ninabwo?” nibaboola mbu: “efwetoto khukhayilesa akamwarumwa ninako ako.”"
  43,25,"Mana nikhubatila khumabii kabakhola, kho hengakhwo, indukho yabakhayi shingala yali"
  43,26,Ne olwa Ibrahim baboolela Samwana nende Abandu bebe mbu; “ toto esie endi ehale nenda kamulaamanga ako.”
  43,27,Halali ulia owalonga niye ulalunjisia
  43,28,"Ne nekhola lino okhuba likhuwa liatong’a khwulwibulo lulwe, bakhababario banyoola okhukalukha"
  43,29,Halali khwasangasia bano nende abebusi babu okhula shiga obwatoto bwaboolela nende Omurumwa Omwinoosi
  43,30,"Ne olwa obwatoto bwaboolela baboola mbu: “ buno ni obulosi ne efwe toto khubukhayile”"
  43,31,"Ne nibaboola mbu: “shichila shina Ikurani ino nileshela khumundu omukhongo mumatokho amakhongo kabili kano?”"
  43,32,"Nohomba abo nibo bakabanga tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi? Efwe khwabakabila obulamu bwabu bwokhushialo hakari wabu, ne nikhuninia abaandi okhushila abaandi khubichelo, kho abaandi banyoole okhukholela abaandi emilimo, ne tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo tsishila bioosi biabakhung’asinjia"
  43,33,"Ne Abandu bakhaya okhuba omukanda mulala, khwakhakholele balia abakhaya Nyasaye tsinzu tsiabu okhuba nende eshitsafu sheifedha, nende tsingasi tsiabu tsiosi tsiabaninilanga"
  43,34,Nende emiliango chietsinzu tsiabu nende ebitanda biabayiekhangakhwo
  43,35,"Nende oburone. Halali ako shinishiosi shiosi tawe, halali ni omwikhoyo kwobulamu bwomushialo muno butswa, ne mwikulu ili ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niyabalia abaria Nyasaye"
  43,36,"Ne ulia wikhola omuwofu khumakhuwa ka Nyasaye, khulamukholela Shetani abe omwitsa wuwe"
  43,37,"Ne totobo babekalilanga injila, ne abeene baparanga mbu balunjika"
  43,38,"Okhula shinga balikhwitsila baliboola mbu: “ oh manyanga oba ehale ninasi shinga ebukwe nende mumbo, oli omwitsa omubii muno.”"
  43,39,"Ne khulwokhuba mbu mwakhola obubii, shibulaho shilabakhoonya enywe olwalelo mbu musanganga mwesi mushinyasio"
  43,40,"Koo onyala okhukhola abekala amarwi bawulila, nohomba onyala okhulunjisia abawofu bali mubukori bwahabulafu"
  43,41,"Ne kata nikhukhuhiniaho, efwe khwitsa okhubahelesia likhobo liefu khubo"
  43,42,"Nohomba\tkhulakhwechesia akakhwabalaka, nafu toto khuli nende obunyali khubo"
  43,43,"Mana tilana nende akawafimbulilwa , toto ewe oli khunjila ingololofu"
  43,44,"Netoto kano ni ametsulisio khwiwe nende khubandu bao, ne mulitsa okhurebwa"
  43,45,"Ne reba Abakhwaruma imbeli wuwo mubarumwa befu, koo khwakhola abanyasaye bandi balamwe balali Owetsimbabaasi ? (Nyasaye)"
  43,46,"Ne toto khwaruma Musa nende ebimanyisio biefu khu Firaun nende aboluyali baye, mana naboola mbu: “ esie endi Omurumwa wa Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje biosi” israeil"
  43,47,Olwa yabetsela nende ebimanyisio biefu bachaka okhumutseshela
  43,48,"Ne shikhwabechesia eshimanyisio shiosi shiosi halali eshikhongo muno okhushila eshindi, mana nikhubatila khushinyasio kho banyoole okhukalukha"
  43,49,"Nibaboola mbu: “enywe Abalosi, khusabile Nyasaye indache yayakhulaka,(nakhurusiliaho eshunyasio shino luno) efwe toto khulalunjikha.”"
  43,50,"Olwa khwabarusiliaho eshinyasio esho, habwene nahabwene nifunaka indache"
  43,51,"Firaun nalaanga Abandu bebe nababoolela mbu: “enywe Abandu banje shendi Omwami welitokho lia Misri, ne emialo chino chiburanga hasi wanje, koo shimulolngakhwo tawe?”"
  43,52,"Nohomba esie shendi noluyali okhushila omutakha uno, ulanyala okhurusia amakhuwa obulayi tawe"
  43,53,"Ne shichila shina nakhaya okhufwala ebindu bieyidhahabu, nohomba yetse nende Amalaika halala ninaye bokhumukhoonya"
  43,54,"Mana nabayila Abandu bebe mana nibamufuchilila, toto abo bali Abandu abakori"
  43,55,Olwa bakhusinyisia khwabatila obutinyu mana nikhubasishia mumaatsi boosi
  43,56,Ne nikhubakhola okhuba abaranjilili nende eshilolelo khubandu beyinyuma
  43,57,Ne olwa Omwana wa Mariam yachelasibwa (nende Adam) Abandu bo boopa oluyoka
  43,58,"Mana nibaboola mbu: “ Abanyasaye befu shini abalayi okhushila ye tawe? Ne shibakhuchelasilia bario tawe halali amayinji butswa, ne abo ni Abandu bokhusolana"
  43,59,Naye shali nobunyali tawe halali ni Omusumba wakhwahelesia tsimbabaasi mana nikhumukhola eshilolelo khubana ba
  43,60,Ne khwenyanga khwakharerere Abamalaika khushialo nibaloondana
  43,61,"Ne toto ye (yesu) ni eshimanyisio shieyinyanga yeyindukho. mulakanakana tawe, ne munoonde khwo, ino niyo injila ingolofu"
  43,62,"Ne Shetani alabekalila tawe, toto ye ni Omusuku wenyu owa habulafu"
  43,63,"Ne olwa Yesu yetsa nende ebifune biahabulafu, yaboola mbu: “ abeetsele nende amachesi nende okhubenoosilia kalia akamukabukhanangamwo, kho murie Nyasaye mana muwulile.”"
  43,64,"Toto Nyasaye niye Omulesi wanje nende Omulesi wenyu, kho mumulaame sa yenyene ino niyo injila ingololofu"
  43,65,"Mana emikanda nichikabukhana abeene khubeene, abaane khubalia bakhola amabii khushinyasio shieyinyanga indulu"
  43,66,"Koo shina shiabaliindanga, halali indukho iliitsa mubwifisi nabo nibalamanyile tawe"
  43,67,"Abeetsa inyanga eyo baliba Abasuku, abeene khubeene, halali balia abaria Nyasaye"
  43,68,"Enywe Abasumba banje, shimulaba noburi inyanga yino tawe , neshimulabeelela tawe"
  43,69,Balia Abasuubila ebimanyisio biefu mana nibelekhuula khu Nyasaye. (nibaba abasalamu)
  43,70,Injile mwikulu enywe nende abakhaye benyu musangasibwemwo
  43,71,"Balibotokhanilibwa ebisanda nende ebikaye bie idhahabu, ne bilibamwo bia omwoyo kwikomba nende ebisangasia tsimoni, ne enywe mulimenyamwo tsinyaanga tsioosi"
  43,72,Eyo niyo mwikulu (janna) amulihebwa khukamwakholanga
  43,73,Mulibaamwo nende ebiamo ebinji biamulilia
  43,74,Toto abetsimbi baliba mushinyasio shia Jahannam tsinyanga tsioosi
  43,75,"Shibalihulusibwa khushinyasio esho tawe, ne omo baliwesiakhwo omwoyo. (okhurulamwo)"
  43,76,Ne shikhwabakholela amabii tawe halali boo abeene nibo bali abamabii
  43,77,"Ne balikhupa oluyoka nibalanga: “ewe Malik! Boolela Nyasaye wuwo akhufwisie’’ naye alibaboolela mbu: “enywe toto omo butswa nimwamulamenya.”"
  43,78,Toto khwabetsela nende obwatoto halali obunji bwenyu mwali mwakhaya obwatoto
  43,79,"Nohomba babusia amalako kabu, ne toto nefwe babusinjia"
  43,80,"Nohomba baparanga mbu efwe shikhuwulilanga akobwifisi nende kokhumonyana kabu tawe? Eeh tawe, abarumwa befu bali ninabo bahandikanga kabakholanga"
  43,81,"Boola mbu: “ Nyasaye abetsanga nende Omwana nesie wakhabeele weyimbeli okhumulaama.”"
  43,82,"Ni woluyali Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, Nyasaye Omulesi weshisaala, khu koosi kabamureetsangakhwo"
  43,83,Ne baleshe bokoyaane nibabaya okhula shinga balinyoolana nende inyanga yabalakwa
  43,84,Naye niye Nyasaye uli mwikulu nende Nyasaye uli mushialo naye niye Omuchesi Omumanyi muno
  43,85,"Ni woluyali ulia owuli nobwami bwomwikulu nende mushialo nende biosi bilimwo, ne niye uli nobumanyi bwebise bieyindukho ne ewuwe ni amulikalusibwa"
  43,86,Ne abamulaamanga abalali ye babula obunyali bwokhubasabila Omundu eshileshelo. Halali ulia wobuloli bwatoto nabo bamanya
  43,87,"Nenobareeba mbu niwina wabaloongabo, ? toto bweene balaboola mbu ni: “ Nyasaye” kho ni hena abakalukhanibungwa"
  43,88,"Ne okhuboola khukhwe (Omurumwa) mbu : “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi bano ni Abandu balasuubila tawe.”"
  43,89,Baleshele ne obaboolele amakhuwa komuleembe. Baliitsa okhumanya